== Births == * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3 (Intercalary May) (Gregorian calendar {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|1846|ja|1846th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Princess Kazunomiya|ja|和宮親子内親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , eighth daughter of {{ill|Emperor Ninkō|ja|仁孝天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and wife of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemochi|ja|徳川家茂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1877|ja|1877th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). == Deaths == * {{ill|Emperor Suizei|ja|綏靖天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 33 (Julian calendar {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|549 BC|ja|紀元前549th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Emperor Suizei|ja|綏靖天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 2nd {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
