* {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=}}  3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}}  {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|qq=}} , {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|qq=}}  fired upon American merchant ships anchored in the {{ill|Shimonoseki Strait|ja|下関海峡|qq=}} .
