== Events == * {{ill|Keiun|ja|慶雲|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|June 16|ja|6月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|704|ja|704th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - The era name changed from {{ill|Taihō|ja|大宝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to Keiun due to auspicious cloud omens. * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Chōshū Domain|ja|Chōshū Domain|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} fired upon American merchant ships anchored in the {{ill|Shimonoseki Strait|ja|下関海峡|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - The {{ill|New Currency Act|ja|新貨条例|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} was promulgated, adopting the decimal system and establishing "yen, sen, and rin" as currency units. The old 1 ryo was set equal to 1 yen.
== Births == * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3 (Intercalary May) (Gregorian calendar {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|1846|ja|1846th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Princess Kazunomiya|ja|和宮親子内親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , eighth daughter of {{ill|Emperor Ninkō|ja|仁孝天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and wife of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemochi|ja|徳川家茂|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1877|ja|1877th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). == Deaths == * {{ill|Emperor Suizei|ja|綏靖天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 33 (Julian calendar {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|549 BC|ja|紀元前549th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Emperor Suizei|ja|綏靖天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 2nd {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . == See Also ==
