== Births == * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōka|qq=}} 3 (Intercalary May) (Gregorian calendar {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 3|qq=}} , {{ill|1846|ja|1846th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1846|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Princess Kazunomiya|ja|和宮親子内親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Princess Kazunomiya|qq=}} , eighth daughter of {{ill|Emperor Ninkō|ja|仁孝天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Ninkō|qq=}} and wife of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemochi|ja|徳川家茂|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iemochi|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1877|ja|1877th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1877|qq=}} ). == Deaths == * {{ill|Emperor Suizei|ja|綏靖天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Suizei|qq=}} 33 (Julian calendar {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 10|qq=}} , {{ill|549 BC|ja|紀元前549th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/549 BC|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Emperor Suizei|ja|綏靖天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Suizei|qq=}} , 2nd {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor of Japan|qq=}} . == See Also ==
